05&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.tbray.org/ongoing/When/200x/2005/12/13/MS-vs-Google&#34;&gt;Time Bray has it right&lt;/a&gt;. In the future, every site can carry search. All Microsoft has to do is to give the revenues from any potential search to the site carrying it. Two big assumptions:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
